Hi, I'm Richard,
a course developer at Udacity.

00:00:03.580 --> 00:00:05.490
After reviewing some of the feedback for
this course,

00:00:05.490 --> 00:00:09.180
Cameron asked me to help him add
an additional lesson on jQuery events.

00:00:09.180 --> 00:00:10.510
So here we are.

00:00:10.510 --> 00:00:13.250
